'''汉密尔顿山'''（{{lang-en|Mount Hamilton}}）是美国[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[圣克拉拉县|圣克拉拉县]][[代阿布洛岭|代阿布洛岭]]的一座山。这座山高度为{{Convert|4265|ft|m}}，俯瞰高度城市化的[[圣克拉拉谷|圣克拉拉谷]]。山顶有世界上第一个永久性有人居住的山顶<ref>{{Cite web|title=U.S. Geological Survey Publications Warehouse|url=http://pubs.usgs.gov/|accessdate=2015-12-18|work=pubs.usgs.gov|archive-date=2014-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108105538/http://pubs.usgs.gov/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[天文台|天文台]][[利克天文台|利克天文台]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Building of Lick Observatory|url=http://collections.ucolick.org/archives_on_line/bldg_the_obs.html|accessdate=2011-05-08|work=Historical Collections Project|publisher=The Link Observatory|archive-date=2014-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141122082258/http://collections.ucolick.org/archives_on_line/bldg_the_obs.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 1899年发现的[[小行星|小行星]][[小行星452|452 Hamiltonia]]以此山命名。在汉密尔顿山的山坡上有发现[[金雕|金雕]]筑巢点。天气晴朗时，从山顶可以看到{{link-en|塔玛尔派伊斯山|Mount Tamalpais}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rntl.net/mthamiltonlookout.htm |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-11-20 |archive-date=2021-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410210230/http://rntl.net/mthamiltonlookout.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>、{{link-en|圣克鲁斯山|Santa Cruz Mountains}}、[[蒙特雷湾|蒙特雷湾]]、{{link-en|蒙特雷半岛|Monterey Peninsula}}，甚至[[优胜美地国家公园|优胜美地国家公园]]。<ref>[http://www.geoscapesphotography.com/Bay_Nature.html Special Project - Bay Nature http://web.archive.org/web/20190708133031/http://www.geoscapesphotography.com/Bay_Nature.html] {{Wayback|url=http://www.geoscapesphotography.com/Bay_Nature.html |date=20160704202938 }} (archived at the [[Wayback_Machine|Wayback Machine]])</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.flickr.com/photos/equanimity/8258974951/ |title=Monterey Peninsula from Mt. Hamilton |access-date=2020-11-20 |archive-date=2019-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190112221533/https://www.flickr.com/photos/equanimity/8258974951/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://meandmyconnie.wordpress.com/tag/lick-observatory/ |title=Lick Observatory Blog Entry |access-date=2020-11-20 |archive-date=2018-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180121071234/https://meandmyconnie.wordpress.com/tag/lick-observatory/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

